title: The Sandbox: Land Purchase
body:
MutantCats is going into The Sandbox! That was decided in the last purchase Snapshot, so now, lets decide which plot of land shall we. 

We've been researching together as a community getting different plots of lands. When we look for a 6x6 the most important is location. Here are two options that we must consider. The first one has the advantage of being were every player is going to spawn in the future, the second one is at the north close to kong island.


1. Land in the center were you spawn, close to biggest Atari plot of land

https://ibb.co/mymnwPr

Price: 65 eth (The offer may need to increase since the prices are increasing in real time and he says he got offered 90eth. This last thing may not be true and the offer may not be real yet)



2. Land in the north, close to CK, touching a 24x24 and near Binance

https://ibb.co/5kGxwjh

Price:  78 eth (He cannot guarantee this price if we wait much more, as he consideres already this a really good price since the floor right now is 1.8 for one plot of land)
